regions.title: Major side damage to white car
regions.description: This region covers the large, clearly visible impact and deformation on the driver-side doors and lower panel of the white car, with metal crumpling, deep dents, and broken glass.

summary: All valid, high-confidence cells are grouped into a single large region corresponding to severe side impact damage on the white car. Two low-confidence edge cells were removed for lack of clear damage. There is no evidence of visually separate damage regions.
